{"tid":2030153,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蓬佩奧譴責北京任意推行香港國安法 強調美國站在港人一方","createTime":"2020-05-22T14:56:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T16:05:57.000Z","uid":21470,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"872e14d1d3f86c9edcf98ca1c4042dc02fb82277","tid":2030153,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:56:46.000Z","msg":"蓬佩奧譴責北京任意推行香港國安法 強調美國站在港人一方<br />\n22.05.2020 22:50<br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧發聲明，譴責北京在香港，單方面及任意推行香港國安法，強調會站在香港人一方。蓬佩奧批評，北京的決定繞過香港立法程序，並忽視香港人的意願，等同為高度自治敲響喪鐘。蓬佩奧指，香港已發展成一座自由堡壘，美國強烈敦促北京重新考慮這項災難性提案，強調任何損害香港自治和自由的決定，無可避免會影響美國對一國兩制及香港地位的評估。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1289514&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1289514%26csid%3D261_341&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CAexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=2089d720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1289514&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"ee3afe5bd9c45668d129d75afa9c314e4f80dfe0","tid":2030153,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:57:00.000Z","msg":"「524遊行前」需要解決既四件事<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2030135\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2030135</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c9ae5a063edb57bf414d629b8adef994e817a171","tid":2030153,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:57:06.000Z","msg":"站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61f041b504d13b14a14bedb924fcb4c7c291873a","tid":2030153,"uid":25105,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:59:09.000Z","msg":"有冇人想我一樣好掙扎<br />\n你見到加速主義好撚爽<br />\n<br />\n但同時你又覺得因為已經犧牲左好多人<br />\n美國仲唔出手好sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ec33317934cd8eead9b9102b9b73c95f54a8962","tid":2030153,"uid":127862,"like":0,"dislike":1,"s